I18N.Title: WCOM
I18N.Translation: The 'Commercial information' frame is a URL pointing at a webpage with information such as where the album can be bought. There may be more than one "WCOM" frame in a tag, but not with the same content.

I18N.Title: WCOP
I18N.Translation: The 'Copyright/Legal information' frame is a URL pointing at a webpage where the terms of use and ownership of the file is described.

I18N.Title: WOAF
I18N.Translation: The 'Official audio file webpage' frame is a URL pointing at a file specific webpage.

I18N.Title: WOAR
I18N.Translation: The 'Official artist/performer webpage' frame is a URL pointing at the artists official webpage. There may be more than one "WOAR" frame in a tag if the audio contains more than one performer, but not with the same content.

I18N.Title: WOAS
I18N.Translation: The 'Official audio source webpage' frame is a URL pointing at the official webpage for the source of the audio file, e.g. a movie.

I18N.Title: WORS
I18N.Translation: The 'Official internet radio station homepage' contains a URL pointing at the homepage of the internet radio station.

I18N.Title: WPAY
I18N.Translation: The 'Payment' frame is a URL pointing at a webpage that will handle the process of paying for this file.

I18N.Title: WPUB
I18N.Translation: The 'Publishers official webpage' frame is a URL pointing at the official wepage for the publisher.
